item.title: Some one help fix
item.dc:creator: @V_1_N_C_H V 1 N C H
item.description:
@V_1_N_C_H wrote:

Since I directed you to this client I know what one it is

copy the hybridpvpnetcache folder, paste it somewhere and make it a zip file (hybridpvpnetcache.zip) Put it in dropbox (Dropbox.com) public folder and get the link. Then go to cachedownloader.java in the client folder and change this private String cacheLink = "http://hybridpvp.net/cache.zip"; // Link to cache with private String cacheLink = "DROPBOX PUBLIC LINK HERE"; // Link to cache (Replace “DROPBOX PUBLIC LINK HERE” with the actual link.) and remake the webclient. (The dropbox public link will look something like this: https://dl.dropbox.com/u/97996038/hybridpvpnetcache.zip)
